name: Consumer Club
description: Consumer Club is an exclusive, application-only community for founders building consumer apps. With 300+ vetted members generating over $500M in annual revenue, it offers a high-signal environment for collaboration. The community spans both venture-backed and bootstrapped founders, with backing from YC, a16z, Neo, Pear VC, and more. Members connect via Discord, biweekly masterminds, and in-person events. The median member earns $1M in ARR, creating unmatched peer insight and support.
